Text: WHAT IN WANT TO SHOW  IN THIS TRAVEL STORY THAT IN ORDER TO LIVE IN HARMONY
  AND EXIST IN CULTURALLY CONVERGENT(NOT ONE CULTURE DISAPPEARING UNDER ANOTHER) WE
  CAN CO EXIST AS JUST HUMANS  WITH OUR WAYS OF LIVING OR IDEAS OF CULTURE LIVING
  THE PAST BEHIND US AND KNOWING THAT WE ARE ALL EQUAL BEINGS LIVING WITH UNITY IN
  DIVERSITY AND WE CAN SHOW THIS BY TELLING THE ANGOLAN AND OTHER DESCENDANTS THAT
  LIVE IN PORTUGAL AND THE EXPERIENCES THEY SHARE TOGETHER
